Behind the Code

Hey there, I see you've managed to claw yourself away from my code and want to see what the fuss is all about. My name's Nathaniel Reline, but I prefer Nathan or Nate. If you couldn't tell, I'm a programmer and I love it. I specialize in Android programming using Java and sometimes C++. I built this website myself from the ground up as some proof of my web programming skills and am more than comfortable in a Linux environment.


Let's get personal. I'm years old, born in California, raised in Germany, and currently live in Arizona. I can speak conversational Japanese und ein bisschen Deutsch, and love to get away from my desk and play soccer every once in a while. My favorite bands are Red Hot Chili Peppers, Foo Fighters, and Gorillaz. If you'd like to get to know me some more or just say hey, please feel free to contact me on my cell or shoot me an email.
